<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-2773] Vagrant provision fails if num_brokers or num_zookeepers is nonzero</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2773</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Changes to vagrant provisioning for kafka system tests updated the default path from &quot;kafka&quot; to &quot;kafka-trunk&quot; on the vagrant virtual machines.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We neglected to update the corresponding path in vagrant/broker.sh and vagrant/zk.sh. Therefore provisioning a static kafka cluster with Vagrant currently fails.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix here is just to update the corresponding path in vagrant/broker.sh and vagrant/zk.sh&lt;/p&gt;</description>
